definitions.definition: A habitational surname from Old Norse .
A suburb of Sydney , New South Wales , Australia .
A local government area in north Sydney , New South Wales ; in full, Hornsby Shire .
A town in Hardeman County , Tennessee , United States .
A hamlet in Cumwhitton parish, Carlisle district, Cumbria , England ( OS grid ref NY5150 ) .
